{
  "stem": "12494.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was interesting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it used to be-- there used to be Jew beating at Hungarian universities, ever since World War I.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But by the time I got to the university, the number of Jews at the university was so small that the majority dispensed with beating us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our seniors reported to us that in the '30s there used to be regular Jew beating, but there was none during the less than a year that I went to the university.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was discrimination.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to sit in the last row, of the lectures that we attended.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was not a requirement of the university-- the university was officially neutral.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the university treated us like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But there was the Hungarian Students' Association, which was extremely right-wing, and very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they made it clear, on the first day that we attended the so-called reception ceremonies, that the Jews have to sit in the last row, unless they want to be beaten up.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said-- this was said publicly-- there was a big reception meeting, where the-- the rector of the school, [NON-ENGLISH], the president welcomed us, and a bunch of professors spoke.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then they left and then came the representatives of the student association.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And their first statement was, are there any Jews here?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were three or four of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, stand up, and we stood up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said, you always will sit in the last row, go up there to the last row.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and then they started singing anti-Jewish songs, and that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they didn't bother us, otherwise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- there was no beating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, that's the way I got to the university.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I attended the lectures and took my examinations.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
